   R.E. Cachau, J. Chem. Phys., in press.

   "Computational Studies of the Domain Movement and the Catalytic
   Mechanism of Thymidine Phosphorylase," S.W. Rick, Y.G. Abashkin, R.L.
   Hilderbrandt, and S.K. Burt, Proteins, 37, 242 (1999).

   "Molecular Mechanisms of Resistance: Free Energy Calculations of
