   I.A. Topol, J.W. Erickson, and S.K. Burt, Protein Science, 7, 1750
   (1998).

   "Reaction Path and Free Energy Calculations of the Transition Between
   Alternate Conformations of HIV-1 Protease," S.W. Rick, J.W. Erickson,
   and S.K. Burt, Proteins, 32, 7 (1998).

   "Reply to Comment on `Electrostatic Potentials and Free Energies of
