   Garcia, S. Garde, B.J. Berne, and S.W. Rick, J. Phys. Chem. B, 102,
   3841 (1998).

   "Constructing Ab Initio Force Fields for Molecular Dynamics
   Simulations," Y.-P. Liu, K. Kim, B.J. Berne, R.A. Friesner, and S.W.
   Rick, J. Chem. Phys., 108, 4739 (1998).

   "The Free Energy of the Hydrophobic Interaction from Molecular Dynamics
   Simulations: the Effects of Solute and Solvent Polarizability," S.W.
   Rick and B.J. Berne, J. Phys. Chem. B,101, 10488 (1997).

   "Electrostatic Potentials and Free Energies of Solvation of Polar and
   Charged Molecules," G. Hummer, L.P. Pratt, A.E. Garcia, B.J. Berne, and
   S.W. Rick, J. Phys. Chem. B, 101, 3017 (1997).

   "Dynamical Fluctuating Charge Force Fields: the Aqueous Solvation of
   Amides," S.W. Rick and B.J. Berne, J. Am. Chem. Soc., 118, 672 (1996).
